java.lang

Class Class<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Class<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AnnotatedElement, GenericDeclaration, Type

    public final class Class<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable, GenericDeclaration, Type, AnnotatedElement
    MJI model class for java.lang.Class library abstraction This is a JPF specific version of a system class because we can't use the real, platform VM specific version (it's native all over the place, its field structure isn't documented, most of its methods are private, hence we can't even instantiate it properly). Note that this class never gets seen by the real VM - it's for JPF's eyes only. For now, it's only a fragment to test the mechanism, and provide basic class.getName() / Class.ForName() support (which is (almost) enough for Java assertion support
    See Also:
